summary:
Natalia is a real estate expert with a broad knowledge of commercial property market (specialising in retail), economics, management and finance. During her 7 years in Jones Lang Lasalle she provided advice on development and improvement of the retail commercial schemes as well as financial analysis and recommendation on potential and ongoing projects. After joining Unibail-Rodamco-Westfield corporate leasing team in 2015 she gained a wide knowledge of international retail environment and built strong connections with many intercontinental, regional and local brands. Currently she works as a Head of Portfolio at Rituals where she is responsible for the optimisation of the existing portfolio.   
Apart from real estate, retail and sustainability she is passionate about travel, cooking (and eating!!!), playing with her dog and spending time with her friends.
